basicCard.title: The Flu or Influenza
basicCard.subtitle: Covered
basicCard.formattedText:
The flu Is covered.  RediCare VIP  covers outpatient treatment of colds and flu. You should call the RediCare VIP Telemedicine or go to either the RediCare VIP primary care physician or the urgent care clinic.
The common cold, including chest cold and head cold, and seasonal flu are caused by viruses. Use over-the-counter cold medications to relieve symptoms including sore throat, runny nose, congestion, and cough. Flu symptoms are similar, but include fever, headache and muscle soreness. Some severe cases may require hospitalization which is not covered by RediCare VIP.
